{"arkId":"cl010104128","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010104128","modified ":"2025-08-25","title":"Montre octogonale","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Montre octogonale"}],"displayDateCreated":"Epoque \/ p\u00e9riode : Louis XIII (1610-1643) (Occident-\u003E\u00e9poque moderne = Ancien R\u00e9gime-\u003Edynastie des Bourbons)\r\n\r\nDate de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1600 - 1625","currentLocation":"Richelieu, [OArt] Salle 531 - Paul Garnier, Vitrine 2","room":"Salle 531, Aile Aile Richelieu, Niveau 1","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1600,"endYear":1625,"imprecision":"","text":"1er quart du XVIIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Cuper, Michel","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","dates":[{"date":"1632","place":"","type":"date de mort"}],"creatorRole":"Horloger","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"OA 10051","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"horlogerie ; montre","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Montre octogonale ; bo\u00eetier octogonal \u00e0 deux couvercles, \u00e0 pans coup\u00e9s, mont\u00e9s \u00e0 charni\u00e8re. Couvercle du cadran orn\u00e9 d\u0027un m\u00e9daillon central de forme octogonale figurant Dana\u00e9; sur le pourtour, deux femmes nues, deux Amours et deux oiseaux apparaissent dans des m\u00e9daillons trap\u00e9zo\u00efdaux. Face oppos\u00e9e repr\u00e9sentant V\u00e9nus et l\u0027Amour ainsi que des figurines. Plaque du cadran grav\u00e9e de figures log\u00e9es dans huit compartiments (chim\u00e8res, satyre, lapin). Anneau horaire \u00e0 chiffres romains encadrant le dieu Pan. Echappement \u00e0 verge, fus\u00e9e avec corde \u00e0 boyau. Cliquet reperc\u00e9 et grav\u00e9 de rinceaux fleuris ; coq disparu.","inscriptions":"Inscription : \r ; int\u00e9rieur des couvercles : Johanna\/Hu\u00ffch-Spaen\r ; Signature : \r ; mouvement sign\u00e9 : Michel Cuper\/ABlois","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"4,5","displayDimension":"4,5 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"3","displayDimension":"3 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Epaisseur","value":"2,2","displayDimension":"2,2 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : argent\r\nMat\u00e9riau : laiton","placeOfCreation":"Blois (Centre-\u003ELoir-et-Cher = Loir et Cher)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Collection Fr\u00e9d\u00e9ric Spitzer (1815-1890) ; collection Emile Artus vente Paris, galerie Charpentier 16-17 mai 1950 n\u00b0 148 ; collection Claudius C\u00f4te (1881-1956), Lyon ; legs Mme Marie-Fran\u00e7oise C\u00f4te, accept\u00e9 par d\u00e9cret du 9 juillet 1961","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[{"value":"Mme C\u00f4te, Marie-Fran\u00e7oise","note":"","role":", Donateur"},{"value":"M. C\u00f4te, Claudius","note":"","role":", Collectionneur"},{"value":"M. Spitzer, Fr\u00e9d\u00e9ric","note":"","role":", Collectionneur"}],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"legs","doubt":"","dates":[{"type":"date du legs","value":"1961","startYear":1961,"endYear":1961},{"type":"date de comit\u00e9\/commission","value":"02\/02\/1961","startYear":1961,"endYear":1961},{"type":"date du conseil","value":"16\/02\/1961","startYear":1961,"endYear":1961},{"type":"date du d\u00e9cret","value":"09\/07\/1961","startYear":1961,"endYear":1961}]}],"ownedBy":"Etat","heldBy":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, D\u00e9parteme